05:09.309 --> 05:10.435
THANK YOU.

05:10.477 --> 05:12.687
BUT I REALIZE...

05:12.729 --> 05:17.734
THAT IT WAS JUST BEFORE

05:12.729 --> 05:17.734
THE CANCER TOOK MOM.

05:17.776 --> 05:19.945
YOU KNOW, I TRIED TO HELP HIM

05:17.776 --> 05:19.945
WITH THE BILLS.

05:19.987 --> 05:22.906
HE SWORE HE HAD IT

05:19.987 --> 05:22.906
UNDER CONTROL.

05:22.948 --> 05:24.116
[ SNIFFLES ]

