I COULD HAVE STOPPED THIS!

05:25.450 --> 05:26.660
WELL, NO, NO, LISTEN.

05:26.701 --> 05:28.369
THIS GUY DOYLE --

05:26.701 --> 05:28.369
HE'S A -- HE'S A LOAN SHARK.

05:28.411 --> 05:29.913
I DON'T THINK

05:28.411 --> 05:29.913
YOU COULD HAVE HELPED.

05:29.955 --> 05:32.373
BUT MAYBE WE CAN.

05:29.955 --> 05:32.373
HUH?

05:32.415 --> 05:36.086
NO, HE WANTS $15,000

05:32.415 --> 05:36.086
IN THE NEXT TWO HOURS,

05:36.128 --> 05:37.712
NATE, OR HE'S TAKING THE BAR.

05:37.754 --> 05:39.756
